</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-%EC%A7%80%EC%A0%95\">타입 지정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#primitive-type%EA%B3%BC-reference-type\">Primitive type과 Reference Type</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%EC%9D%98-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94\">변수의 초기화</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#%EC%BD%94%ED%8B%80%EB%A6%B0%EC%9D%98-null\">코틀린의 Null</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#elvis-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%9E%90\">Elvis 연산자</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#%ED%94%8C%EB%9E%AB%ED%8F%BC-%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85\">플랫폼 타입</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%ED%83%80%EC%9E%85-null/#reference\">📚Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"2023년 01월 18일","title":"[Kotlin] 코틀린의 변수와 null","tags":["Kotlin"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Kotlin/20230118-Kotlin-변수타입-null/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Spring/20221218-모모팀-서비스성능-개선기4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"모모팀 서비스 성능 개선기4 (비동기 처리를 통한 장애 전파 제거)"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["3911196313","4111100897"]}